		<tr>
		    <td valign="top">
		     <p><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Article Title:</b>&nbsp;</font>
		     <font face="Verdana" size="2">Customer Service Policy Review</font><br>
		     <a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=507845" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		
		<tr><td>&nbsp;</tr><tr>
		
		    <td valign="top">
		    <p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    John Smedley started a new thread yesterday in the <a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/Forum1/HTML/000354.html">Developer's Corner</a> regarding Customer Service policies for Everquest.  Apparently their has been a major review of the SoE Customer Service policies and they want some feedback form customers:<br>
<blockquote>
  Hello All,
  <p>In the past few weeks we have been doing a full review of our Customer
  Service policies and procedures from top to bottom. On Wednesday October 24th,
  we will be announcing these changes on EverQuest.com. At this point we would
  like to ask our customers what things they would like to see changed to make
  sure our own thoughts are in line with our player base.
  <p>Please send any suggestions or thoughts on this to policyfeedback@soe.sony.com.
  <p>John Smedley<br>
  Chief Operating Officer<br>
  Sony Online Entertainment<br>
  </p>
</blockquote>


		    </font></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
